{"lang": "zh_TW", "eventid": "main_15", "eventName": "解離重組", "entryType": "MAINLINE", "storyCode": "15-7", "avgTag": "行動後", "storyName": "臨界時刻", "storyInfo": "卡特斯感染者得知了自己所在艦船的主人名叫“普瑞賽斯”。博士在阿米婭跨越邊界，遭遇危險時來到阿米婭的身邊，兩人相互扶持繼續前行。\n", "storyList": [{"id": 0, "prop": "HEADER", "attributes": {"key": "title_test", "is_skippable": "true", "fit_mode": "BLACK_MASK"}}, {"id": 1, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 2, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 3, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 4, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "60_g2_rhodeslivingroom_bc", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 5, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 6, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 7, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"key": "$wasteland_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 8, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 9, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "卡特斯從未覺得毀滅，尤其是能清晰感受到逼近的毀滅，是一件能夠被坦然接受的事實。"}}, {"id": 10, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 11, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1719_1#9$1", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 12, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 13, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我、我做不到親歷所愛的一切被摧毀之後還能無動於衷。", "name": "希爾達"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1719_1#9$1"}, {"id": 14, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我無法理解您——", "name": "希爾達"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1719_1#9$1"}, {"id": 15, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_cosmicelfvoice"}}, {"id": 16, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1720_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 17, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "並非無動於衷，而是相信宇宙的絕對平等。可惜，你來得稍晚了一些。", "name": "神秘的精靈"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1720_1#1$1"}, {"id": 18, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這艘艦船剛剛在數萬光年外，目睹了一次超新星爆炸，並順利逃離。", "name": "神秘的精靈"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1720_1#1$1"}, {"id": 19, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "若是你能親眼見到那個景象，或許就更能理解我的意思。", "name": "神秘的精靈"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1720_1#1$1"}, {"id": 20, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 21, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "大廳內的儀器開始快速地轉動，直到卡特斯無法再用肉眼捕捉到它的軌跡。"}}, {"id": 22, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "然後，她看到了許多浮動的光影出現。"}}, {"id": 23, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1719_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 24, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我看到了一個發射暗淡深紅色光芒的巨大球體，而另一個靛藍色的小點也在球體的表面飛速掠過。", "name": "希爾達"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1719_1#1$1"}, {"id": 25, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但是，又好像是那個很大的球體正繞著那個很小的藍點旋轉？", "name": "希爾達"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1719_1#1$1"}, {"id": 26, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1720_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 27, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你口中的藍點就是剛剛經歷了超新星爆炸的脈衝星。", "name": "神秘的精靈"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1720_1#1$1"}, {"id": 28, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那個正逐漸被撕扯的紅色恆星曾是它的同伴，如今也正走向不可逆轉的死亡。", "name": "神秘的精靈"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1720_1#1$1"}, {"id": 29, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "它們曾帶來了許多有趣的原始生命，我也十分懷念在那個星系的行星中漫步的經歷。", "name": "神秘的精靈"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1720_1#1$1"}, {"id": 30, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "可惜那些生命甚至尚未來得及看到天空之外的世界就迎來了死亡。", "name": "神秘的精靈"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1720_1#1$1"}, {"id": 31, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1719_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 32, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……您為何要向我展示這些？", "name": "希爾達"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1719_1#1$1"}, {"id": 33, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1720_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 34, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "只是在共享我們所擁有的知識，旅客。", "name": "神秘的精靈"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1720_1#2$1"}, {"id": 35, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "片面的偏執與無知往往是有效資訊傳遞的障礙之一，我對你的來歷同樣無知。", "name": "神秘的精靈"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1720_1#2$1"}, {"id": 36, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 37, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "卡特斯已經無暇去理解眼前之人的話，猛然間，她所觸及的新知識開始衝擊她的思維。"}}, {"id": 38, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1719_1#9$1"}}, {"id": 39, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "大地……可能會誕生兩次生命？這些從天空墜下的星星……也會帶來生命？", "name": "希爾達"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1719_1#9$1"}, {"id": 40, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "“毀滅”的盡頭……並非絕望。", "name": "希爾達"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1719_1#9$1"}, {"id": 41, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們……於那片大地而言並不特殊？", "name": "希爾達"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1719_1#9$1"}, {"id": 42, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1720_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 43, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "一顆足以供養生命的星球會平等地愛著所有生活其上的生物，無論生命發源於何處。這是自然的規律。", "name": "神秘的精靈"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1720_1#1$1"}, {"id": 44, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不要過度貪婪地汲取那些你還無法完全理解的知識。", "name": "神秘的精靈"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1720_1#1$1"}, {"id": 45, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1719_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 46, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我在其中也看到了您的身影，您的身邊也曾有許多同族，但突然——", "name": "希爾達"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1719_1#1$1"}, {"id": 47, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "“幽靈”，很多人這樣稱呼您，對吧？", "name": "希爾達"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1719_1#1$1"}, {"id": 48, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1720_1#3$1"}}, {"id": 49, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我的確只是一個遊蕩的幽靈。如我所言，當真正的毀滅降臨於我和我的同族面前時，我也無能為力。", "name": "幽靈"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1720_1#3$1"}, {"id": 50, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1719_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 51, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……您所說的毀滅到底是什麼？", "name": "希爾達"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1719_1#1$1"}, {"id": 52, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我已經在這裡看到了太多分明是神明才能實現的手段，到底是怎樣的毀滅才能威脅到你們？", "name": "希爾達"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1719_1#1$1"}, {"id": 53, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1720_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 54, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "旅客，你的問題，恐怕這艘船上無人能夠回答。", "name": "幽靈"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1720_1#1$1"}, {"id": 55, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哪怕在你的眼中，我們所擁有的知識足以被寰宇中眾多的生命視作“神明的手段”……", "name": "幽靈"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1720_1#1$1"}, {"id": 56, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但宇宙之浩瀚，我們所能探索的領域也同樣存在極限。", "name": "幽靈"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1720_1#1$1"}, {"id": 57, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1719_1#10$1"}}, {"id": 58, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "希爾達"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1719_1#10$1"}, {"id": 59, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1720_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 60, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你很失落？", "name": "幽靈"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1720_1#1$1"}, {"id": 61, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1719_1#10$1"}}, {"id": 62, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "所以絕不可能存在一個永恆的國度，一個人人都能獲得無盡幸福和快樂的樂園？", "name": "希爾達"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1719_1#10$1"}, {"id": 63, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1720_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 64, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你希望這樣的國度存在嗎？", "name": "幽靈"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1720_1#2$1"}, {"id": 65, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 66, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "卡特斯猶豫片刻後，點了點頭。"}}, {"id": 67, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1720_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 68, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "沒有生靈是永恆的。我所熟知的歷史中，也有過傳奇的文明征服了千萬個星系，他們在宇宙中漫步的時光跨越百萬年之久。", "name": "幽靈"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1720_1#1$1"}, {"id": 69, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "可於宇宙而言，他們留下的痕跡終究還是渺小不堪。", "name": "幽靈"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1720_1#1$1"}, {"id": 70, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們都曾迷失在盲目追求不存在的信條與理想的……不可追憶的黃金時代中，我們都堅信自我的存在有著絕對的目的。", "name": "幽靈"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1720_1#1$1"}, {"id": 71, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但最終呢？", "name": "幽靈"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1720_1#1$1"}, {"id": 72, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1719_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 73, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "希爾達"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1719_1#2$1"}, {"id": 74, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1720_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 75, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "任何一個誕生靈智的生命都曾執著於宣揚自我為所處世界的中心，但是否有可能，對宇宙而言——", "name": "幽靈"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1720_1#1$1"}, {"id": 76, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "自始至終，我們無足輕重。這才是瞭解宇宙之前所必須學會的第一課。", "name": "幽靈"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1720_1#1$1"}, {"id": 77, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "記得你剛剛所見的那場絢麗的超新星爆發嗎？", "name": "幽靈"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1720_1#1$1"}, {"id": 78, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "生命終會在墳墓中再次誕生，而終有一天，他們會理解我們在墓碑上刻下的印記。", "name": "幽靈"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1720_1#1$1"}, {"id": 79, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那是我們曾經擁有的生活。我們存在過。", "name": "幽靈"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1720_1#1$1"}, {"id": 80, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1719_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 81, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……我無法理解您的話。", "name": "希爾達"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1719_1#1$1"}, {"id": 82, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那我們是如何在那片大地上誕生的？", "name": "希爾達"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1719_1#1$1"}, {"id": 83, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在我們之前，是否也曾誕生過更加輝煌的文明？", "name": "希爾達"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1719_1#1$1"}, {"id": 84, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1719_1#10$1"}}, {"id": 85, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "而我們是否也會在目所能及的未來迎接毀滅？", "name": "希爾達"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1719_1#10$1"}, {"id": 86, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "還有我更在意的，源石所帶來的疾病與痛苦，是否也能得到根除？", "name": "希爾達"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1719_1#10$1"}, {"id": 87, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我請求您指引我找到通往這些知識的道路……", "name": "希爾達"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1719_1#10$1"}, {"id": 88, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1720_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 89, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我無法回答你任何一個問題。你的前三個問題在宇宙中有著不同語言的不同版本，它們只能由你們自身回答。", "name": "幽靈"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1720_1#1$1"}, {"id": 90, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "而最後一個問題……很抱歉，我從未聽說過“源石”，也並未從已有的資料庫中搜尋到任何與“源石”相關的資訊。", "name": "幽靈"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1720_1#1$1"}, {"id": 91, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1719_1#9$1"}}, {"id": 92, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "——？", "name": "希爾達"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1719_1#9$1"}, {"id": 93, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1720_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 94, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不過，我認識一位有趣的人，也是這艘艦船的主人。或許她能解答你的疑惑。", "name": "幽靈"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1720_1#1$1"}, {"id": 95, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1719_1#9$1"}}, {"id": 96, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這艘艦船的主人？", "name": "希爾達"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1719_1#9$1"}, {"id": 97, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1720_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 98, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "也是一位聲名遠揚的語言學家，她叫——", "name": "幽靈"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1720_1#1$1"}, {"id": 99, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 100, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 101, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 102, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 103, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 104, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "“普瑞賽斯”。"}}, {"id": 105, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 106, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "60_g6_crownboundary", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 107, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 108, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"key": "$faceoff_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 109, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1037_amiya3_1#6$2"}}, {"id": 110, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "博士，現在不是發呆的時候！", "name": "阿米婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_1037_amiya3_1#6$2"}, {"id": 111, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "抓緊我！", "name": "阿米婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_1037_amiya3_1#6$2"}, {"id": 112, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 113, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 114, "prop": "Decision", "attributes": {"options": "——！;阿米婭，你看到了嗎？", "values": "1;2"}, "targetLine": {"option1": "line115", "option2": "line115"}}, {"id": 115, "prop": "Predicate", "attributes": {"references": "1;2"}, "endOfOpt": false}, {"id": 116, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1037_amiya3_1#6$2"}}, {"id": 117, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我暫時不敢分心，編織一條通向奇點的道路很困難。", "name": "阿米婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_1037_amiya3_1#6$2"}, {"id": 118, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哪怕有特蕾西婭小姐的協助……", "name": "阿米婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_1037_amiya3_1#6$2"}, {"id": 119, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "博士，你看到了什麼！", "name": "阿米婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_1037_amiya3_1#6$2"}, {"id": 120, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 121, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 122, "prop": "Decision", "attributes": {"options": "……", "values": "1"}, "targetLine": {"option1": "line123"}}, {"id": 123, "prop": "Predicate", "attributes": {"references": "1"}, "endOfOpt": false}, {"id": 124, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 125, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你看到了一個熟悉的身影。"}}, {"id": 126, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 127, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 128, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 129, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {"image": "50_i16", "screenadapt": "coverall", "fadetime": 0.0}}, {"id": 130, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 131, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 132, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.6, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 133, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "去吧，“博士”，去解開你的困惑。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 134, "prop": "subtitle", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 135, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 136, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 137, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 138, "prop": "Decision", "attributes": {"options": "……", "values": "1"}, "targetLine": {"option1": "line139"}}, {"id": 139, "prop": "Predicate", "attributes": {"references": "1"}, "endOfOpt": false}, {"id": 140, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 141, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 142, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 143, "prop": "image", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 144, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1037_amiya3_1#1$2"}}, {"id": 145, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "60_g6_crownboundary", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 146, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 147, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 148, "prop": "Decision", "attributes": {"options": "不必分心，阿米婭。;執行我們原本的計劃。;繼續搭建這座“橋”！", "values": "1;2;3"}, "targetLine": {"option1": "line149", "option2": "line149", "option3": "line149"}}, {"id": 149, "prop": "Predicate", "attributes": {"references": "1;2;3"}, "endOfOpt": false}, {"id": 150, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1037_amiya3_1#6$2"}}, {"id": 151, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "好！我正在努力穩定每一個連接點，博士。", "name": "阿米婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_1037_amiya3_1#6$2"}, {"id": 152, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "凱爾希醫生之前搜尋的每一項記錄都被特蕾西婭小姐標記了出來，我正試圖將它們串聯起來。", "name": "阿米婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_1037_amiya3_1#6$2"}, {"id": 153, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但我還需要一個錨點，一個能夠指引我返回的錨點——", "name": "阿米婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_1037_amiya3_1#6$2"}, {"id": 154, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4134_cetsyr_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 155, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我會於此守望，我會成為你的錨點。", "name": "魔王"}, "figure_art": "avg_4134_cetsyr_1#1$1"}, {"id": 156, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "繼續前進吧，阿米婭。", "name": "魔王"}, "figure_art": "avg_4134_cetsyr_1#1$1"}, {"id": 157, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 158, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 159, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 160, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 161, "prop": "bgeffect", "attributes": {"name": "$eb_confusion_centra", "layer": 1.0}}, {"id": 162, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {"image": "60_i05", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 163, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_messageconverge_loop", "loop": "true", "channel": "s", "volume": 0.0}}, {"id": 164, "prop": "SoundVolume", "attributes": {"volume": 1.0, "channel": "s", "fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 165, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 166, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 167, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "粉紅色的絲線開始聚集。"}}, {"id": 168, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "蜿蜒的線條交織盤旋，逐漸從邊界開始向更遠處延伸。"}}, {"id": 169, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "超越邊界，通往奇點的通路正逐漸形成。"}}, {"id": 170, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "成功了！", "name": "阿米婭"}}, {"id": 171, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "雖然源石技藝在這裡似乎並不奏效，但是藉由源石技藝的施術邏輯來重構這裡出現的資訊是可行的！", "name": "阿米婭"}}, {"id": 172, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 173, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 174, "prop": "Decision", "attributes": {"options": "你可以做到呼叫完全未知的資訊搭建“橋”？", "values": "1"}, "targetLine": {"option1": "line175"}}, {"id": 175, "prop": "Predicate", "attributes": {"references": "1"}, "endOfOpt": false}, {"id": 176, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不行，這裡充斥著我無法解析，甚至連“文明的存續”都無法替我轉譯的資訊，完全依靠我自己無法構建通路。", "name": "阿米婭"}}, {"id": 177, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但好在凱爾希醫生的存取留下了記錄，她的研究數據在特蕾西婭小姐的協助下能夠被我捕捉到。", "name": "阿米婭"}}, {"id": 178, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這就足夠了。", "name": "阿米婭"}}, {"id": 179, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "粉紅色的絲線緩慢地盤旋串聯起諸多龐雜的數據，那是凱爾希留下的足跡。"}}, {"id": 180, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "由一絲到千絲萬縷，道路正逐漸浮現。"}}, {"id": 181, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 182, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "“凱爾希，我能感知到你的情緒。”", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 183, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "“以我擅自對你構建的情緒模型得出的數據分析，你的緊張情緒並不僅僅來自我所展示出的特蕾西婭形象，你有更加在意的事情。”", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 184, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "“我會試著調整。我並不希望我個人的情緒變化干擾任何後來者在查詢這些記錄時的客觀判斷。”", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 185, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "“但你的情緒仍然在波動，凱爾希。你在害怕？”", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 186, "prop": "subtitle", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 187, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "構建通路的效率不高，但應該能奏效。", "name": "阿米婭"}}, {"id": 188, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我想嘗試進入通路，嘗試向奇點靠近。", "name": "阿米婭"}}, {"id": 189, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 190, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 191, "prop": "Decision", "attributes": {"options": "我陪你一起。", "values": "1"}, "targetLine": {"option1": "line192"}}, {"id": 192, "prop": "Predicate", "attributes": {"references": "1"}, "endOfOpt": false}, {"id": 193, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "“是的，我在害怕。”", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 194, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "“我害怕自己留下的資訊最終無法被阿米婭和博士準確捕獲，也害怕——”", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 195, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "“若是事態已經惡化到不得不採取這樣的極端手段，我留下的線索也已不再算得上有益的協助——”", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 196, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "“或是錯誤地引導求知者直面了我最不願提及的威脅。”", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 197, "prop": "subtitle", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 198, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不，博士，我不會允許你在我尚未探明情況的前提下貿然進入通路。", "name": "阿米婭"}}, {"id": 199, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 200, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 201, "prop": "Decision", "attributes": {"options": "阿米婭……", "values": "1"}, "targetLine": {"option1": "line202"}}, {"id": 202, "prop": "Predicate", "attributes": {"references": "1"}, "endOfOpt": false}, {"id": 203, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "原諒我的堅持，但這就是我的決定。", "name": "阿米婭"}}, {"id": 204, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 205, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 206, "prop": "StopSound", "attributes": {"channel": "s", "fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 207, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_messagesuccess"}}, {"id": 208, "prop": "effect", "attributes": {"name": "$e_confusion_connect", "layer": 2.0}}, {"id": 209, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 5.0}}, {"id": 210, "prop": "bgeffect", "attributes": {"name": "$eb_confusion_loop", "layer": 3.0}}, {"id": 211, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "千絲萬縷的資訊所構建的通路已經遠遠延伸到了奇點。"}}, {"id": 212, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "阿米婭毫不猶豫地踏上了通路，她第一次涉足了邊界之外——"}}, {"id": 213, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 214, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_messagewave"}}, {"id": 215, "prop": "ImageTween", "attributes": {"xScaleTo": 1.1, "yScaleTo": 1.1, "duration": 2.0}}, {"id": 216, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {"image": "60_i05", "screenadapt": "coverall", "fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 217, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 218, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "浪湧。"}}, {"id": 219, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……？", "name": "阿米婭"}}, {"id": 220, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這種感覺，就好像這些資訊形成了實質的浪湧一樣，怎麼會——", "name": "阿米婭"}}, {"id": 221, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 222, "prop": "Decision", "attributes": {"options": "恐怕這只是開始。;“越靠近奇點，資訊的密度會越高”……", "values": "1;2"}, "targetLine": {"option1": "line223", "option2": "line223"}}, {"id": 223, "prop": "Predicate", "attributes": {"references": "1;2"}, "endOfOpt": false}, {"id": 224, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "果然如特蕾西婭小姐所言，這裡的資訊已經足以產生質量。", "name": "阿米婭"}}, {"id": 225, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "繼續深入應該會受到更大的阻礙。", "name": "阿米婭"}}, {"id": 226, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 227, "prop": "Decision", "attributes": {"options": "阿米婭，先撤回來。;我們需要考慮更好的應對方法。", "values": "1;2"}, "targetLine": {"option1": "line228", "option2": "line228"}}, {"id": 228, "prop": "Predicate", "attributes": {"references": "1;2"}, "endOfOpt": false}, {"id": 229, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我沒辦法保證穩定住這條脆弱的通路，深入其中的消耗遠比我預期的要更大。", "name": "阿米婭"}}, {"id": 230, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我必須繼續向前，只要沿著凱爾希醫生留下的那些信標……", "name": "阿米婭"}}, {"id": 231, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "提卡茲走入的銀色山脈從她的身邊掠過，墜入冰原的巨獸投下的漆黑陰影轉瞬即逝。"}}, {"id": 232, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "阿米婭所看到的畫面仍在快速從她的身邊掠過，彷彿她正逆向蹚著時間的河流向前。"}}, {"id": 233, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "越來越多她無法理解，無法描述的畫面衝擊著她的思維。"}}, {"id": 234, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她努力封鎖那些無邊無際卻又混亂不堪的資訊。"}}, {"id": 235, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "集中注意力，集中注意力，只需要注視著凱爾希醫生留下的信標……前進……", "name": "阿米婭"}}, {"id": 236, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "只要能觸碰到奇點——", "name": "阿米婭"}}, {"id": 237, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 238, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 239, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 1.0, "g": 1.0, "b": 1.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 240, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 241, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 242, "prop": "bgeffect", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 243, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {"image": "60_i02", "xScale": 1.3, "yScale": 1.3, "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 244, "prop": "ImageTween", "attributes": {"duration": 30.0}}, {"id": 245, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 246, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 247, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "無聲的寂靜。"}}, {"id": 248, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "阿米婭甚至無法聽到自己呼吸的聲音。"}}, {"id": 249, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "——？！", "name": "阿米婭"}}, {"id": 250, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這是……什麼地方？", "name": "阿米婭"}}, {"id": 251, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那個巨大的球體……在碎裂？", "name": "阿米婭"}}, {"id": 252, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "崩解的球體讓她感到眩目，而那艘飄浮在空中的奇異形狀的艦船更是讓她恍了恍神。"}}, {"id": 253, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "到底……發生了什麼？", "name": "阿米婭"}}, {"id": 254, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "為什麼我會看到——", "name": "阿米婭"}}, {"id": 255, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "而就在她恍神之際，一顆轉動的巨石以一種緩慢卻不可阻擋的趨勢向阿米婭逼近。"}}, {"id": 256, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "——！", "name": "阿米婭"}}, {"id": 257, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 258, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 3.0, "xstrength": 15.0, "ystrength": 20.0, "vibrato": 40.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 259, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 260, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 261, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 262, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "黑色的陰影迅速遮擋了阿米婭的全部視線，她下意識地試圖保護自己，但隨即而來的卻是無法控制的墜落感。"}}, {"id": 263, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "失敗了嗎……是資訊的浪湧嗎？"}}, {"id": 264, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "“阿米婭！”"}}, {"id": 265, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……博士……？", "name": "阿米婭"}}, {"id": 266, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 267, "prop": "Decision", "attributes": {"options": "我在。", "values": "1"}, "targetLine": {"option1": "line268"}}, {"id": 268, "prop": "Predicate", "attributes": {"references": "1"}, "endOfOpt": false}, {"id": 269, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$shatterpoint_02_intro", "key": "$shatterpoint_02_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 270, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "阿米婭感覺到有一隻手扶住了自己，支撐著自己的思維保持穩定。"}}, {"id": 271, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 272, "prop": "Decision", "attributes": {"options": "試著封鎖那些干擾我們的資訊。;我和你一起。", "values": "1;2"}, "targetLine": {"option1": "line273", "option2": "line273"}}, {"id": 273, "prop": "Predicate", "attributes": {"references": "1;2"}, "endOfOpt": false}, {"id": 274, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 275, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 276, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 277, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {"image": "60_i04", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 278, "prop": "ImageTween", "attributes": {"xScaleFrom": 1.0, "yScaleFrom": 1.0, "xScaleTo": 1.2, "yScaleTo": 1.2, "duration": 100.0}}, {"id": 279, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"xstrength": 3.0, "ystrength": 2.0, "vibrato": 20.0, "randomness": 60.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 280, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 281, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 282, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 283, "prop": "Decision", "attributes": {"options": "希望我來得不算晚。;抱歉沒能乖乖聽你的話，阿米婭。", "values": "1;2"}, "targetLine": {"option1": "line284", "option2": "line284"}}, {"id": 284, "prop": "Predicate", "attributes": {"references": "1;2"}, "endOfOpt": false}, {"id": 285, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "博士……太好了……", "name": "阿米婭"}}, {"id": 286, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "剛剛那一瞬間……", "name": "阿米婭"}}, {"id": 287, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 288, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_messagewave"}}, {"id": 289, "prop": "ImageTween", "attributes": {"xScaleTo": 1.05, "yScaleTo": 1.05, "duration": 2.0}}, {"id": 290, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {"image": "60_i04", "screenadapt": "coverall", "fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 291, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 292, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你竭力支撐阿米婭搖晃的身體，自奇點噴發而出的資訊浪湧依舊不斷衝擊著你們。"}}, {"id": 293, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "近乎形成實體的資訊沖刷過你們的思維，在虛空中留下了混雜不清的殘影——"}}, {"id": 294, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那是已然逝去的過去，是被龐大資訊記錄的當下，也似乎是預知了你們下一步行動的未來。"}}, {"id": 295, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "可惜眼下，你們並沒有多餘的精力再去關注這些。"}}, {"id": 296, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "從這裡回望邊界，你們已經不知不覺在通路上前行了很遠，而奇點……"}}, {"id": 297, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "奇點近在眼前。"}}, {"id": 298, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "博士，你看到剛才那個恐怖的景象了嗎？", "name": "阿米婭"}}, {"id": 299, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 300, "prop": "Decision", "attributes": {"options": "看到了。;我無法分辨其中的含義。", "values": "1;2"}, "targetLine": {"option1": "line301", "option2": "line301"}}, {"id": 301, "prop": "Predicate", "attributes": {"references": "1;2"}, "endOfOpt": false}, {"id": 302, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我十分肯定那不是發生在泰拉的景象……", "name": "阿米婭"}}, {"id": 303, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 304, "prop": "Decision", "attributes": {"options": "但至少這意味著我們的確正在接近奇點。;更多的資訊正在向我們開放。", "values": "1;2"}, "targetLine": {"option1": "line305", "option2": "line305"}}, {"id": 305, "prop": "Predicate", "attributes": {"references": "1;2"}, "endOfOpt": false}, {"id": 306, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 307, "prop": "Decision", "attributes": {"options": "你還撐得住嗎，阿米婭？", "values": "1"}, "targetLine": {"option1": "line308"}}, {"id": 308, "prop": "Predicate", "attributes": {"references": "1"}, "endOfOpt": false}, {"id": 309, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "當、當然。", "name": "阿米婭"}}, {"id": 310, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 311, "prop": "Decision", "attributes": {"options": "……", "values": "1"}, "targetLine": {"option1": "line312"}}, {"id": 312, "prop": "Predicate", "attributes": {"references": "1"}, "endOfOpt": false}, {"id": 313, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你很清楚你們如今的處境，儘管你知道這樣可能收效甚微，但你還是下意識地伸出手，試圖擋在阿米婭的前面。"}}, {"id": 314, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 315, "prop": "Decision", "attributes": {"options": "這裡的衝擊更多針對思維，我能應付。;我走前面。", "values": "1;2"}, "targetLine": {"option1": "line316", "option2": "line316"}}, {"id": 316, "prop": "Predicate", "attributes": {"references": "1;2"}, "endOfOpt": false}, {"id": 317, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 318, "prop": "Decision", "attributes": {"options": "關於我們要找的關鍵，我有了線索。", "values": "1"}, "targetLine": {"option1": "line319"}}, {"id": 319, "prop": "Predicate", "attributes": {"references": "1"}, "endOfOpt": false}, {"id": 320, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 321, "prop": "Decision", "attributes": {"options": "我收集並演算了凱爾希留下的存取記錄。", "values": "1"}, "targetLine": {"option1": "line322"}}, {"id": 322, "prop": "Predicate", "attributes": {"references": "1"}, "endOfOpt": false}, {"id": 323, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 324, "prop": "Decision", "attributes": {"options": "直接從我的思維裡讀取關鍵資訊。", "values": "1"}, "targetLine": {"option1": "line325"}}, {"id": 325, "prop": "Predicate", "attributes": {"references": "1"}, "endOfOpt": false}, {"id": 326, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 327, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "找到了。", "name": "阿米婭"}}, {"id": 328, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "以關鍵字“安眠橋”為篩選條件，凱爾希醫生進行了共計七萬九千三百四十六次搜尋……", "name": "阿米婭"}}, {"id": 329, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "雖然所有的搜尋都與“源石”有關，但按照博士你的推測，這些數據都與源石的本質並無太大關聯。", "name": "阿米婭"}}, {"id": 330, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "如果結果都是拒絕存取而毫無收穫，線索豈不是完全中斷了？", "name": "阿米婭"}}, {"id": 331, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 332, "prop": "Decision", "attributes": {"options": "並非如此。", "values": "1"}, "targetLine": {"option1": "line333"}}, {"id": 333, "prop": "Predicate", "attributes": {"references": "1"}, "endOfOpt": false}, {"id": 334, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 335, "prop": "Decision", "attributes": {"options": "凱爾希會重複搜尋同一個條目多次。", "values": "1"}, "targetLine": {"option1": "line336"}}, {"id": 336, "prop": "Predicate", "attributes": {"references": "1"}, "endOfOpt": false}, {"id": 337, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 338, "prop": "Decision", "attributes": {"options": "這本身就是在向我們傳遞某種資訊。", "values": "1"}, "targetLine": {"option1": "line339"}}, {"id": 339, "prop": "Predicate", "attributes": {"references": "1"}, "endOfOpt": false}, {"id": 340, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "重複搜尋？等等，重複的搜尋次數組成的無限循環的代碼也能夠被解密？", "name": "阿米婭"}}, {"id": 341, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……博士，你已經解出了答案。", "name": "阿米婭"}}, {"id": 342, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 343, "prop": "Decision", "attributes": {"options": "是的，一個熟悉的名字。", "values": "1"}, "targetLine": {"option1": "line344"}}, {"id": 344, "prop": "Predicate", "attributes": {"references": "1"}, "endOfOpt": false}, {"id": 345, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 346, "prop": "Decision", "attributes": {"options": "或許是一個指示……;或許是一個警告……", "values": "1;2"}, "targetLine": {"option1": "line347", "option2": "line347"}}, {"id": 347, "prop": "Predicate", "attributes": {"references": "1;2"}, "endOfOpt": false}, {"id": 348, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "阿米婭"}}, {"id": 349, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我從未聽說過這個名字，無論是你還是凱爾希醫生，都從來沒有說起過——", "name": "阿米婭"}}, {"id": 350, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "“普瑞賽斯”？", "name": "阿米婭"}}, {"id": 351, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 352, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 353, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 1.0, "g": 1.0, "b": 1.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 354, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 355, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 356, "prop": "image", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 357, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.1, "xstrength": 3.0, "ystrength": 2.0, "vibrato": 20.0, "randomness": 60.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 358, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_white", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 359, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 1.0, "g": 1.0, "b": 1.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 360, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 361, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "<color=#000000>………………</color>", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 362, "prop": "subtitle", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 363, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "——博士，我們看到的是同一個畫面嗎？", "name": "阿米婭"}}, {"id": 364, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 365, "prop": "Decision", "attributes": {"options": "……恐怕，是的……", "values": "1"}, "targetLine": {"option1": "line366"}}, {"id": 366, "prop": "Predicate", "attributes": {"references": "1"}, "endOfOpt": false}, {"id": 367, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 368, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 1.0, "g": 1.0, "b": 1.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 369, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 370, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {"image": "avg_ac8mi_Pre", "screenadapt": "coverall", "fadetime": 0.0}}, {"id": 371, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"key": "$monastery_sad_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 372, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 1.0, "g": 1.0, "b": 1.0, "fadetime": 3.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 373, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 374, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "“普瑞賽斯……”"}}, {"id": 375, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你從未見過這個畫面，更沒有見過——"}}, {"id": 376, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（未知語言）你來了，{@nickname}。", "name": "普瑞賽斯"}}, {"id": 377, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 378, "prop": "Decision", "attributes": {"options": "那是……？;“我”……？", "values": "1;2"}, "targetLine": {"option1": "line379", "option2": "line379"}}, {"id": 379, "prop": "Predicate", "attributes": {"references": "1;2"}, "endOfOpt": false}, {"id": 380, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（未知語言）改進你設計出來的PRTS花了點時間。", "name": "預言家"}}, {"id": 381, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（未知語言）我以為你去休息了。", "name": "預言家"}}, {"id": 382, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（未知語言）不，我一直在想你剛剛說的話。", "name": "普瑞賽斯"}}, {"id": 383, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（未知語言）“不存在描述神的語言，因為神本身的存在是絕對不可理解的。”", "name": "普瑞賽斯"}}, {"id": 384, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（未知語言）你很清楚那只是我們漫無目的聊天時的隨口之言。", "name": "預言家"}}, {"id": 385, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（未知語言）如果我假設這是一個正確的前提。", "name": "普瑞賽斯"}}, {"id": 386, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（未知語言）以此為出發點，創造一種足夠描述神的語言，是否也意味著神能夠被我們理解？", "name": "普瑞賽斯"}}, {"id": 387, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（未知語言）難道你不為此而激動嗎？", "name": "普瑞賽斯"}}, {"id": 388, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（未知語言）也許我們為了找到那個問題的答案，一直都走在了錯誤的道路上——試圖藉助宇宙已經誕生的規則去解讀宇宙的本質。", "name": "普瑞賽斯"}}, {"id": 389, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（未知語言）你想用完全由我們所創造的語言去解釋宇宙。一個過於大膽的設想，普瑞賽斯。", "name": "預言家"}}, {"id": 390, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（未知語言）哈哈，是嗎？", "name": "普瑞賽斯"}}, {"id": 391, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她乾脆俐落地用手指在空中畫出一個無比標準的菱形。"}}, {"id": 392, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（未知語言）那乾脆就從現在開始，如何？", "name": "普瑞賽斯"}}, {"id": 393, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 394, "prop": "Decision", "attributes": {"options": "……", "values": "1"}, "targetLine": {"option1": "line395"}}, {"id": 395, "prop": "Predicate", "attributes": {"references": "1"}, "endOfOpt": false}, {"id": 396, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "博士，他們在討論什麼？", "name": "阿米婭"}}, {"id": 397, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你早已見過眼前之人，在內化宇宙中，她曾陪伴在你的身旁——"}}, {"id": 398, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 399, "prop": "Sticker", "attributes": {"id": "st1", "multi": "true", "text": "但我很確信……{@nickname}……", "x": 220.0, "y": 250.0, "alignment": "left", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 800.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 400, "prop": "Sticker", "attributes": {"id": "st1", "multi": "true", "text": "\\n\\n當你真正對一切感到困惑的時候，你會想起——答案一直都在這裡。", "size": 24.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 401, "prop": "Sticker", "attributes": {"id": "st1", "multi": "true", "text": "\\n\\n我在這裡。", "size": 24.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 402, "prop": "Sticker", "attributes": {"id": "st1", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 403, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 404, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}